      <div class="section__wrap section__decorations"> 
       <div class="section__content section__content--centered"> 
        <h3 class="title"> <span class="lol-text lol-text--centered">The Curse</span> <small class="title__sub">Of The Sad Mummy</small> </h3> 
        <p>Every child in Valoran has heard the tale before,<br> About the cursed mummy boy who felt his heart no more.<br> So sad and lorn, the helpless lad, Amumu was his name,<br> He ventured out to find a friend and learn about his bane.</p> 
        <a href="http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/creative-spotlight/curse-sad-mummy" class="btn btn--cta section__btn"><span class="btn__content">Discover</span></a> 
       </div>

     </section>

     <section class="section section--frequencies section--trans"> 
      <div class="section__wrap section__decorations"> 
       <div class="section__content"> 
        <h3 class="title"> <span class="lol-text">Frequencies</span> <small class="title__sub">Documentary</small> </h3> 
        <p>Join us behind the scenes and discover the moments that helped create The Curse of the Sad Mummy and the music of League. From the first notes of a piano melody scrawled in a notebook to anthems and epics inspired by the League of Legends universe, watch as the Riot Games music team forges new musical sagas through passion, collaboration, and the pursuit of creative harmony</p> 
        <a href="http://frequencies.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/frequencies/" class="btn btn--cta section__btn"><span class="btn__content">Watch Now</span></a> 
       </div>

        </div> 
       </div>
       <!-- /.section__aside --> 
       <div class="section__content"> 
        <h3 class="title"> <span class="lol-text">Pentakill</span> <small class="title__sub">Smite &amp; Ignite</small> </h3> 
        <p>You have seen the true voice of metal fall quiet, surrounded by the massed harmonies of your weak whispers. But listen closely to those whispers, and you shall find the seed of truth. Four voices. Five harbingers of destruction, waiting patiently for their time to rise.</p> 
        <a href="http://na.pentakillmusic.com/en/" class="btn btn--cta section__btn"><span class="btn__content">Headbang Now</span></a>
